feat/scoring-and-display:
    ✔ Handle tied team scores - return rank field from backend so front end can display order. @started(26-06-09 15:04) @done(26-06-09 15:42) @lasted(38m56s)
        Solution: map over the results and check how many existed with the highest score, return an array of strings for team names. 
    ✔ Scoring inputs must be number type only. @done(26-06-09 20:41)
    ✔ When input exited with no score, default to empty not 0. @done(26-06-09 21:09)
        Solution: store the input value as a string in state instead of a number, only converting to a number when calculating totals. This way, an empty input stays empty ("") rather than defaulting to 0. Extra input props added, apparently they are redundent but lets test them - inputMode="numeric" pattern="[0-9]*"
